OL,3,CCouple left daughter to die in 'most
OL,4,Cinhumane way possible', court hears
OL,6,FThe parents of a woman who died in an
OL,7,Femaciated state left her to "fade into
OL,8,Finsignificance", a court has heard.
OL,10,FSteffie Davies, 32, was found dead by
OL,11,Fparamedics who were called to her home
OL,12,Fin Wrexham in May 2023, Mold Crown
OL,13,FCourt heard on Wednesday (18 March).
OL,15,FHer parents, Alan and Bernita Davies -
OL,16,Fboth 60, admitted causing or allowing
OL,17,Fthe death of their daughter, who had
OL,18,Fanxiety and rarely left the house.
OL,26,@oD@]OUpD@OO]
