PN,46902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1774012288
OL,3,CCouple left daughter to die in 'most
OL,4,Cinhumane way possible', court hears
OL,6,FMs Davies was "almost skeletal", with
OL,7,Fpressure sores and joint contractures
OL,8,Fthat would have prevented her from
OL,9,Feating or drinking without assistance.
OL,10,FAndrew Jones KC, prosecuting, said she
OL,11,Fhad dirty matted hair, with possible
OL,12,Flice eggs in, suspected fungal
OL,13,Finfections on her skin and the bed she
OL,14,Fwas found in was "sodden".
OL,16,FIn a statement, Ms Davies' sister said
OL,17,Fshe had shown potential at college,
OL,18,Fwhere she studied animal care, but her
OL,19,Fanxiety grew as she got older and she
OL,20,Ffound it hard to leave the house.
OL,26,@nD@OOUnD@_O]vD@ROUvD@YO]
