OL,3,CCouple left daughter to die in 'most
OL,4,Cinhumane way possible', court hears
OL,6,FThe older sibling, who was not named
OL,7,Fin court and had been estranged from
OL,8,Ftheir parents for a number of years,
OL,9,Fsaid: "With the right support and
OL,10,Fencouragement from my mum and dad, she
OL,11,Fcould have done so much with her life.
OL,13,F"Instead she was left to fade into
OL,14,Finsignificance in the most inhumane
OL,15,Fway possible. No sentence could ever
OL,16,Fbe able to atone for that."
OL,26,@qD@GOUuD@AOUxD@[O]
