OL,3,CCouple left daughter to die in 'most
OL,4,Cinhumane way possible', court hears
OL,6,FDistressing photos of her injuries
OL,7,Fwere not shown in court after Mrs
OL,8,FJustice Stacey said she wanted to
OL,9,F"preserve, if possible, some of
OL,10,FSteffie's dignity in death".
OL,12,FThe court heard a recording of the 999
OL,13,Fcall made by Mrs Davies to report her
OL,14,Fdaughter's death at about 8:30am on
OL,15,FMay 26 2023. Mrs Davies could be heard
OL,16,Fcrying in the call, in which she told
OL,17,Fan operator her daughter was "cold"
OL,18,Fand "like a skeleton".
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@[O]yD@^OUyD@cO]zD@EOUzD@UO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/9
