PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1774012288
OL,3,CCouple left daughter to die in 'most
OL,4,Cinhumane way possible', court hears
OL,6,FMr Jones said Mrs Davies told officers
OL,7,Fshe attended to her daughter at 9pm on
OL,8,FMay 24 2023, when she was in bed
OL,9,Freading, and checked on her a number
OL,10,Fof times the following day when she
OL,11,Fappeared to be asleep, before finding
OL,12,Fher dead on May 26.
OL,14,FMr Jones said: "In all probability,
OL,15,Fshe had been dead long before that."
OL,17,FThe court heard it was not possible to
OL,18,Festablish when Ms Davies died but
OL,19,Fulcers on her body had been there for
OL,20,Fat least six weeks, according to an
OL,21,Fexpert.
OL,26,@vD@POUwD@dO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/9
