OL,3,CCouple left daughter to die in 'most
OL,4,Cinhumane way possible', court hears
OL,6,FMs Davies, recorded as weighing five
OL,7,Fstone nine pounds and being five foot
OL,8,Fseven inches tall, died from sepsis
OL,9,Fdue to infected pressure ulcers, very
OL,10,Flow body weight and poor nutritional
OL,11,Fstatus, a pathologist found. Her
OL,12,Fground floor bedroom was in an
OL,13,F"appalling state", in a "marked
OL,14,Fcontrast" to the clean condition of
OL,15,Fthe rest of the home, Mr Jones said.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@QO]uD@YOUvD@IO]
