OL,3,CCouple left daughter to die in 'most
OL,4,Cinhumane way possible', court hears
OL,6,FMr and Mrs Davies, who both made no
OL,7,Fcomment in police interviews, were
OL,8,Finitially charged with gross
OL,9,Fnegligence manslaughter - but guilty
OL,10,Fpleas to the charge of causing or
OL,11,Fallowing their daughter's death were
OL,12,Faccepted earlier this year.
OL,14,FMaria Masselis, defending Mrs Davies,
OL,15,Fsaid: "The defendant's plea is a
OL,16,Fpublic acknowledgement that she failed
OL,17,Fher daughter in terms of providing
OL,18,Fadequate care. That's a responsibility
OL,19,Fthat will stay with her for the rest
OL,20,Fof her life."
OL,26,@wD@GOU|D@MO]
