OL,3,CCouple left daughter to die in 'most
OL,4,Cinhumane way possible', court hears
OL,6,FThe court heard the couple had been
OL,7,Ftogether for 34 years and had three
OL,8,Fchildren. Simon Rogers, defending Mr
OL,9,FDavies, said: "This is not a case
OL,10,Fwhere the defendant felt any
OL,11,Fmalevolence towards Steffie, there is
OL,12,Fno ill feeling towards her, he never
OL,13,Fwished her harm, yet he must accept
OL,14,Fthat through his inaction that led to
OL,15,Fher death."
OL,17,FThe pair are due to be sentenced on
OL,18,FThursday.
OL,26,@qD@OOUwD@KO]
